('32766', '5', 'Remove from heat and set aside.In a separate skillet or saucepan, melt butter over medium heat. Sprinkle flour into the pan and whisk immediately to evenly mix it into the butter. Cook for a minute or two, then pour in milk and half and half. Continue cooking, whisking constantly, while sauce thickens, about 2 minutes.'),
('32766', '6', 'Add salt, pepper, and cayenne then add the grated cheddar. Stir while cheese melts. Turn off heat.'),
